Q. What if the source file suddenly becomes 500 times larger?
A. I make use a lazy load that should be to process a huge file. The file processing should bbe moved to a another Job
Q. Is the process easy to deploy for an XML or CSV file with similar content?
A. You have as many filehandlers for the different file formats they should implement the FileHandlerInterface interface and will return an array of data.
Q.Suppose that only records of which the credit card number contains three of the same numbers consecutively should be processed, how would you approach that?
A. The collection can be sorted using the credit card number.
